  "briefContent": "# Brief\n\n## Situation\nThere is a decision to make about the next phase of engineering direction. The board should assess whether the path improves leverage, quality, and career or team trajectory.\n\n## Stakes\nThe wrong path can create technical debt, reduce credibility, or limit future options. The right one can compound expertise and output.\n\n## Constraints\nThe path must fit current capacity, learning bandwidth, and the need for durable, explainable work.\n\n## Key Question\nWhat engineering path best compounds capability and leverage over the next several years?\n",
